doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description' content='Integrum Systems builds professional-grade, maintainable systems for research teams, advanced operators, and technical organizations who value reliability, ownership, and long service life.')
        meta(name='author' content='Integrum Systems')

        title Integrum Systems

        // Favicon
        link(rel='icon' type='image/x-icon' href='assets/favicon.ico')

        include includes/css.pug

    body.d-flex.flex-column.h-100

        main.flex-shrink-0

            // Navigation
            include includes/navbar.pug

            // Hero
            header.bg-ink.py-5
                .container.py-5(style='max-width: 1200px;')
                    .row.justify-content-center
                        .col-lg-8.text-center
                            h1.display-5.fw-bolder.text-white.mb-3 Systems built to last.
                            p.lead.mb-4(style="color: rgba(215,222,232,0.75);")
                                | Integrum designs and builds maintainable, inspectable infrastructure for research teams, advanced operators, and early-stage technical organizations.
                            a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.px-4(href='contact.html') Get in touch

            // Differentiators
            section#differentiators.py-5.bg-fog
                .container.py-4(style='max-width: 1200px;')
                    .row.gx-5.gy-4
                        .col-lg-4
                            .d-flex.flex-column.h-100
                                .feature-icon.mb-3
                                    i.bi.bi-layers
                                h2.h5.fw-bolder.mb-2 Maintainable by Design
                                p.mb-0
                                    | Systems built with modular construction, documented internals, and clear upgrade pathways. No forced obsolescence. No hidden dependencies.
                        .col-lg-4
                            .d-flex.flex-column.h-100
                                .feature-icon.mb-3
                                    i.bi.bi-eye
                                h2.h5.fw-bolder.mb-2 Open Where It Matters
                                p.mb-0
                                    | Transparent interfaces, inspectable software, and clear licensing. We publish our constraints and document our tradeoffs.
                        .col-lg-4
                            .d-flex.flex-column.h-100
                                .feature-icon.mb-3
                                    i.bi.bi-diagram-3
                                h2.h5.fw-bolder.mb-2 Engineering-First Discipline
                                p.mb-0
                                    | Stable APIs, versioning rigor, and defined operating constraints. Architecture is conservative by design. Scope is not.

            // Positioning statement
            section.py-5
                .container.py-4(style='max-width: 1200px;')
                    .row.justify-content-center
                        .col-lg-7.text-center
                            h2.fw-bolder.mb-3 A better way to build.
                            p.mb-3
                                | We occupy the space between consumer-grade maker tools and enterprise-locked industrial systems — delivering infrastructure-grade products and services that are open, inspectable, and built for long service life.
                            p.mb-0
                                | We work with research institutions, advanced independent builders, and early-stage technical teams who cannot afford lock-in and will not tolerate sloppy engineering.

            // CTA strip
            section.py-5.bg-primary
                .container.text-center.py-3(style='max-width: 1200px;')
                    h2.fw-bolder.text-white.mb-2 Start a conversation.
                    p.text-white.mb-4(style="opacity: 0.9;")
                        | Whether you have a defined project or an early-stage problem, we engage at the architecture and system level from day one.
                    a.btn.btn-light.btn-lg.px-4(href='contact.html') Contact Integrum


        // Footer
        include includes/footer.pug

        include includes/scripts.pug